Module VetAppointmentPortal
Package com.vetportal.dto

Class ServiceResponse<T>

java.lang.Object
com.vetportal.dto.ServiceResponse<T>
Type Parameters:
T - the type of data being returned
public class ServiceResponse<T> extends Object
A generic wrapper for service-layer responses. Includes the returned data (if any), a message (typically for errors), and a status indicating the result of the operation. Factory methods to simplify the creation of defined and standardized LookupStatus response types (e.g., SUCCESS, NOT_FOUND, CONFLICT, DB_ERROR).
